# Normalize committer/author identities so git log, GitLab, and any
# other tool consistently shows the canonical "Christophe Barlieb"
# name for commits that were authored under a Windows machine name.
# Non-destructive — commit objects themselves are unchanged; this
# file just remaps how those identities are displayed.
